### Room API Test

### 방 생성 (POST /rooms)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/rooms
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "roomName": "함께하는 쇼핑",
  "targetBudget": 500000,
  "syncMode": "FOLLOW",
  "roomMeta": {
    "shoppingPurpose": "친구들과 함께하는 겨울 쇼핑",
    "interestCategories": ["패션", "전자제품", "가구"],
    "headcount": 4,
    "budgetMin": 100000
  }
}

###

### 방 생성 - FREE 모드
POST http://localhost:8080/api/rooms
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "roomName": "자유 쇼핑방",
  "targetBudget": 1000000,
  "syncMode": "FREE",
  "roomMeta": {
    "shoppingPurpose": "각자 원하는 물건 구매",
    "interestCategories": ["도서", "스포츠", "뷰티"],
    "headcount": 2,
    "budgetMin": 50000
  }
}

###

### 방 조회 - ID로 조회 (GET /rooms/{roomId})
GET http://localhost:8080/api/rooms/1

###

### 방 조회 - 초대 코드로 조회 (GET /rooms/code/{roomCode})
GET http://localhost:8080/api/rooms/code/ab

###

### 방 입장 (POST /rooms/join) - 초대 코드로 입장
POST http://localhost:8080/api/rooms/join
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "roomCode": "426302D1",
  "nickname": "게스트1",
  "profileImage": "https://example.com/profile1.jpg"
}

###

### 방 입장
POST http://localhost:8080/api/rooms/join
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "roomCode": "426302D1",
  "nickname": "게스트2"
}

###

### 참여자 목록 조회 (GET /rooms/{roomId}/members)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/rooms/1/members

###

### 방 나가기 (DELETE /rooms/{roomId}/members/{memberId})
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/rooms/1/members/2

###
